撤回逃犯條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">民陣三罷反送中集會</span><br />\n日期：6月17日（星期一）<br />\n集會地點：立法會外<br />\n當日行動：三罷（罷工罷市罷課）<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">（留意返星期一嘅三罷集會係未有時間，要等民陣fb睇下佢地點安排）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核心目標：撤回逃犯條例</span>"},{"pid":"4f1630f8e58d9e89ce23d57f92f2f9856fe67b05","tid":1225283,"uid":168228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2d1ecb1685c4cef7d4ba40d46f5bb7d61d3c28d2","tid":1225283,"uid":45120,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:25:11.000Z","msg":"佢唔俾時限<br />\n咪我地俾時限佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"無時限真係玩撚晒 屌佢老味 仲等佢聽各界意見? 佢要聽就一早聽撚左啦"},{"pid":"06a91e48d08d103d415c91588ea751958eff706c","tid":1225283,"uid":168228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:28:31.000Z","msg":"未撤回都未算成功呀 收皮啦林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931b12c0baeff46d3492f7730e31680c9d45b351","tid":1225283,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f1630f8e58d9e89ce23d57f92f2f9856fe67b05","tid":1225283,"uid":168228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2d1ecb1685c4cef7d4ba40d46f5bb7d61d3c28d2","tid":1225283,"uid":45120,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:25:11.000Z","msg":"佢唔俾時限<br />\n咪我地俾時限佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"無時限真係玩撚晒 屌佢老味 仲等佢聽各界意見? 佢要聽就一早聽撚左啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"唔理啦`<br />\n過左禮拜日遊行<br />\n政府唔撤就再包多次<br />\n禮拜一朝早就係時限"},{"pid":"e321edcac96183bc2faa75af13cb3faf75cac856","tid":1225283,"uid":168228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0533a9f3b4ec0db01c0d89268c61afe561b23c49","tid":1225283,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:29:56.000Z","msg":"個無限期去撚左邊？"},{"pid":"1063b557700bc7befc4d1d0f34156d574a918c08","tid":1225283,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor